name: Fylibs
body:
### Welcome to Fylibs.
Here you can find some useful libraries to help you programming your application. Enjoy them!

### Authors and Contributors
Fylibs is now developed by @fredyk, but you can ask for contributing (read "Support or Contact" section).

### Support or Contact
If have some issue, find any error or just want to contribute, you can notify in the repository (by clicking "View on GitHub") or contact to support@fredykrujjer.com
